filename.description: Auto-generated from date and title. Used in the URL.

fields.name: title
fields.label: Title
fields.description: The headline of your blog post

fields.name: pubDate
fields.label: Publication Date
fields.description: When this post should be published (can be future-dated)

fields.name: description
fields.label: Description
fields.description: A short summary shown in previews and search results (1-2 sentences)

fields.name: author
fields.label: Author
fields.description: Who wrote this post (defaults to "ECEA")

fields.name: category
fields.label: Category
fields.description: announcement = important updates, news = general news, recap = event recaps, article = educational content

fields.name: image
fields.label: Featured Image
fields.description: The main image shown at the top of the post and in previews

fields.name: src
fields.label: Image
fields.description: Upload a JPG or PNG image (recommended: 1200x630px for social sharing)

fields.name: alt
fields.label: Alt Text
fields.description: Describe the image for accessibility (e.g., "Riders at the start line")

fields.name: tags
fields.label: Tags
fields.description: Keywords for filtering and search (e.g., "enduro", "results", "youth")

fields.name: pinned
fields.label: Pinned (Featured)
fields.description: Check to show this post at the top of the blog page

fields.name: draft
fields.label: Draft
fields.description: Check to hide from the public site (uncheck to publish)

fields.name: body
fields.label: Content
fields.description: The main content of your blog post. Use headings, bold, links, and images.

fields.name: title
fields.label: Event Title
fields.description: The name of the event (e.g., "Ice Breaker", "High Steaks")

fields.name: summary
fields.label: Summary
fields.description: A short tagline or description shown on event cards (1-2 sentences)

fields.name: date
fields.label: Event Date
fields.description: The start date of the event

fields.name: endDate
fields.label: End Date
fields.description: Only needed for multi-day events (e.g., 2-day enduros)

fields.name: keyTime
fields.label: Key/Start Time (EST)

fields.name: checkInTime
fields.label: Check-in Time (EST)
fields.description: Enter time in EST (e.g., "7:00 AM", "8:30 AM")

fields.name: location
fields.label: Location
fields.description: Venue name and address (e.g., "BBB Hunting Club, Pemberton, NJ")

fields.name: hostingClubs

fields.description: Club abbreviations (e.g., SJER, DVTR). Add one club per item.

fields.name: eventType
fields.label: Event Type
fields.description: The type of event - determines calendar color and filtering

fields.name: format
fields.label: Format
fields.description: Race format (e.g., "Sprint Enduro", "2-Hour", "Time Keeping"). Leave blank for non-race events.

fields.name: series
fields.label: Series
fields.description: Which series this counts toward (e.g., "Enduro Series", "Hare Scramble Series")

fields.name: closedCourse
fields.label: Closed Course
fields.description: Check if the course is closed to the public during the event

fields.name: gasAway
fields.label: Gas Away
fields.description: Check if gas is available at the venue (gas away = no need to carry extra fuel)

fields.name: gateFee
fields.label: Gate Fee
fields.description: Entry fee for spectators/non-riders (e.g., "$10 per vehicle")

fields.label: Event Image
